Text: Om man inte gillar Ultima Thule betyder det inte automatiskt att den TEKNISKA KVALITÉN är dålig. Idioter.

Inte för att jag lyssnar på Ultima Thule, men jag vet att dom inte är rasister eftersom jag kan skilja på rasism & nationalism (det är mest rasister & anti-rasister som inte kan se skillnad). Låt dom som älskar Sverige älska det utan att bli  kränkta.
Hoppas dom seedar bra på den här torrent'en, det tar ju år och dar på t.ex The Early years, visserligen en annan som har lagt upp den då. Men ändå.
Ultima Thule är så underbart bäst. Tack :)

Where the hell in the ultima thule lyrics did u find nazi propaganda? I found patriotic rhymes about swedish culture and history. In Spain for example, someone who speeks ill of patriotism is a terrorist. In Sweden, other names for patriotism is racism and nationalism. For example www.patriot.nu is a nazi propaganda website. Have you ever heard the song called Gul och blå? That song explains the situation in Sweden and the reactions of people when they see someone carrying a flag. In Swedish: Patriot = Rasist. Thats a big problem. I appreciate the work of anti-fascistic groups although i think the biggest groups are to involved in politics more than anti-fascism. There is as much reason to accuse Ultima Thule for racism as there is to accuse Iron Maiden for satanism. This is just stupid but is suppose that those who are dumb enough to accuse Ultima Thule for nazism are to stupid to understand english.
Det glädjer mig att see människor som Rootsman
